{"tid":257540,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，有冇熟勞工法例嘅巴打","createTime":"2017-05-25T10:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T12:14:09.000Z","uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c566b916a5b511f3c95cbb0fa221faf0f8ac351","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係一個sales<br />\n有一日老闆分咐話佢個熟客會嚟買野<br />\n咁叫我地招呼佢<br />\n咁嗰日我就招呼佢啦<br />\n仲招呼得好好，買左7萬蚊野<br />\n之後比錢時候 ，我就比左公司個𡃁仔碌卡，開單<br />\n碌完卡要噤密碼就親眼見個𡃁仔放番去卡機<br />\n咁我就繼續招呼個客，幫佢入袋執野<br />\n咁執執下野，佢就攞埋公司單比我比個客<br />\n咁我以為佢出code同出單攪掂晒<br />\n咁就送客出門口<br />\n點知第二日，發現碌卡張野無左<br />\n再清機都無呢個交易<br />\n番睇cctv，原來個𡃁仔放完去卡機個base度<br />\n就無理部機，去左攪其他野<br />\n我唸可能係交易唔成功，所以無出紙<br />\n但如果係咁有乜理由出張公司單比我<br />\n就係咁，老闆再聯絡番客<br />\n但個客話要check下有無過數先<br />\n都過左4.5日<br />\n我想問如果個客唔認數<br />\n我係咪需要賠番7萬比公司？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8814be6103ce6696c3b4e39acc147c30bee4076","tid":257540,"uid":25248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"最多三舊<br />\n有錯唔好屌咁大力"},{"pid":"aa40af05f1eaa9fc3b5f092e6d387304a78ec461","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最多三舊<br />\n有錯唔好屌咁大力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但有啲好似又唔係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce20d543aa893c1c517b62f0aeed28e3510fd8c","tid":257540,"uid":37246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"個新仔賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dab251cda0ca7b72498ebcd13c3a8346fe3eaa8","tid":257540,"uid":90419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最多三舊<br />\n有錯唔好屌咁大力</blockquote><br />\n無記錯係3000"},{"pid":"b8e272f59b4eb3ecc2eeadba13209a1bd873c27b","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最多三舊<br />\n有錯唔好屌咁大力</blockquote><br />\n無記錯係3000</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真3幾千，我賠真係無所謂<br />\n但7皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146ff69a965428e52c8565391476a0d0909dc27f","tid":257540,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"300"},{"pid":"69e63eed565f32318ec76fd485c311aa32f8c8d2","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"但有啲就話，每次300，直到賠晒"},{"pid":"424c22593bc073fecf27878a04fc96b7fcbbce74","tid":257540,"uid":66254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"扣糧最多扣三百<br />\n但好似可以要求你另外俾 咁就冇限"},{"pid":"df04e4394712a9a5ac7640dd8408be9fe703ad68","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣糧最多扣三百<br />\n但好似可以要求你另外俾 咁就冇限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我唔比？"},{"pid":"89086fc1a30db207362aeaf4b02d005a884f3bae","tid":257540,"uid":66,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"有公司會走法律罅<br />\n唔會叫你賠<br />\n會叫扣押<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（個陣係某日本公司做，張卡單冇簽名，<br />\n'扣押'左3千幾蚊，信用卡如果順利過數先會係半年後比返錢我）"},{"pid":"f4e09fc50cd06b5c82d8d049d6803815522e7f1d","tid":257540,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有公司會走法律罅<br />\n唔會叫你賠<br />\n會叫扣押<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（個陣係某日本公司做，張卡單冇簽名，<br />\n'扣押'左3千幾蚊，信用卡如果順利過數先會係半年後比返錢我）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家係等個客，睇佢認唔認<br />\n佢唔認就要我賠"},{"pid":"88c8fb0e6dc0dc579b7476d93cad2cbfce854f3b","tid":257540,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo